{"tid":1092554,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韓K聯賽驚現暴力犯規，韓媒稱這是中國足球式的惡行","createTime":"2019-04-05T02:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T11:25:39.000Z","uid":1369,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7242ccaaf412e754a91a685b3821030280add435","tid":1092554,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"北京時間4月3日，韓國K聯賽第5輪，水原三星主場0-0戰平尚州尚武。比賽當中，發生了一次暴力犯規行為。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEYv328.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEYv328.png&h=00804cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時是在比賽第74分鐘，水原三星隊廉基勛正準備接一個飛來的球，尚州尚武隊的金榮彬衝上前去，飛起一腳蹬在了廉基勛的臉上。廉基勛大叫一聲倒在地上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5zjcWB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5zjcWB.gif&h=69785e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國網友稱，這個球幾乎相當於謀殺。也有人認為金榮彬不是故意的。韓國媒體撰文稱，這個動作是&ldquo;少林足球、功夫足球、暴力足球，是中國足球式的殺人行為&rdquo;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puGd1P4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuGd1P4.png&h=35858e26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe18e7bdbe05654e35e84b1cf02cec3aa7c1cdd5","tid":1092554,"uid":243550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78900ba3d7a1426b528330c3fac0d5a86fbe4578","tid":1092554,"uid":77355,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"尚州尚武係軍人隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068c0a73f4a5878f65e033b4db2e50f1963b7067","tid":1092554,"uid":94075,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"非五毛 支那足球式殺人行為？支那講矛應該唔夠佢地黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ff3a07aa8907daec3530909470a2b021f17932","tid":1092554,"uid":173930,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"韓支都是低賤，不會分得那麼細"},{"pid":"82d5451378c918f5f064e8b83e5053ffd2c1f7e8","tid":1092554,"uid":121058,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/260/18979373260/18982798009_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F260%2F18979373260%2F18982798009_600x399.jpg&h=340d6360&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6995034f2c073eb29ab90e179489e952fce19e32","tid":1092554,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32779a30ef3a936dec820e2a68da62e38bef1989","tid":1092554,"uid":7854,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.eurosport.com/2019/01/11/2497674-51852190-2560-1440.jpg?w=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.eurosport.com%2F2019%2F01%2F11%2F2497674-51852190-2560-1440.jpg%3Fw%3D1050&h=387d3b0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3492a573bf168c582ab697b46c0f3b03652260ef","tid":1092554,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6995034f2c073eb29ab90e179489e952fce19e32","tid":1092554,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d5451378c918f5f064e8b83e5053ffd2c1f7e8","tid":1092554,"uid":121058,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/260/18979373260/18982798009_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F260%2F18979373260%2F18982798009_600x399.jpg&h=340d6360&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho